'''Suicide timers''' were a type of timed demolition charge that was used by the [[Lok Revenants/Legends|Lok Revenants]]/[[Mere Resistance]]. [[Nym/Legends|Nym]] and his commando team were known to use this timer on the shield bunkers to deactivate the shield bunkers to render [[Cavik Toth]]'s [[Trihexalon]] production factory vulnerable and destroy it.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]]''

